I-I did good things.

939
00:38:23,796 --> 00:38:25,187
是谁杀了特雷西
Who killed her?

940
00:38:26,616 --> 00:38:28,966
和想要启动潘朵拉的是一个人
The same man that's trying to pull off Pandora.

941
00:38:30,078 --> 00:38:32,361
