You're not going anywhere until you tell me about Pandora.

946
00:38:47,849 --> 00:38:49,057
潘朵拉是什么
What is it?

947
00:38:50,841 --> 00:38:53,517
是我起草的一份白皮书的名字
It was the name of a white paper that I wrote.

948
00:38:53,517 --> 00:38:54,601
